Cross Creek is a country club community located on 267 acres in South Fort Myers. Plan your wedding, luncheon, or special dinner at our beautiful clubhouse. We can accommodate at up to 135 for either plated meals or a buffet.
Cross Creek Country Club is the centerpiece of a lovely, calm and quiet residential community in Central Fort Myers, just minutes from Exit 131 of US I-75. The spacious clubhouse and all of the club amenities comprise the perfect setting for your special reception or event. And the Cross Creek staff is committed to providing your celebration with the utmost attention to details.
Our team is dedicated to assuring that your
event
,
corporate meeting
or
reception
is one that you and your guest will cherish.
Our Chef and his culinary team will work with you to tailor a menu designed to satisfy the palate of your most discerning guests. They will assure the menu will be perfect for your event and your budget.
To complement your
food selections
, we also stock a full selection of wine and spirits. Signature cocktails, craft and draft beers and your specific family favorites are available to personalize and enhance your celebration.
Our event staff pride themselves on assisting with your specific arrangements throughout the entire planning process.  Our team will be present throughout your event to monitor and support every detail allowing you to enjoy the festivities without concern.
Menus, pricing and rental rates vary by the type, size and season. To learn more, contact our restaurant manager, Dave Clark
Call:  (239) 768-1474 or
Email:
Dave@crosscreekfl.com
We look forward to hosting your event at Cross Creek Country Club.
